Warhead looks at the newcomer. He was glad to have no olfactive 
sensors. In fact, he had them removed when he first met Trashcan.

Warhead: Tell me, Trashcan, how did you know we were going to Earth? I 
told no one yet...

His stare was inquisitive, and he wanted it to intimidate the 
wide-load bot.
